<!--
WHEN I click on the dashboard option in the navigation
THEN I am taken to the dashboard and presented with any blog posts I have already created and the option to add a new blog post

WHEN I click on the button to add a new blog post
THEN I am prompted to enter both a title and contents for my blog post

WHEN I click on the button to create a new blog post
THEN the title and contents of my post are saved and I am taken back to an updated dashboard with my new blog post

WHEN I click on one of my existing posts in the dashboard
THEN I am able to delete or update my post and taken back to an updated dashboard
-->
<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <h3 class="m-3">{{user.dataValues.username}}'s dashboard</h3>
</div>
<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" href="/new-post">Create new post</button>
</div>
{{#each posts as |post|}}
<div class="card m-5">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">{{post.dataValues.title}}</h5>
        <p class="card-text">{{post.dataValues.content}}</p>
        <p class="card-text text-muted small">{{format_date post.dataValues.createdAt}}</p>
        <a id="edit" class="m-2">Edit</a>
        <a id="delete" class="m-2">Delete</a>
    </div>
</div>
{{/each}}
<script src="/js/dashboard.js"></script>